page.title: 11Families - Louise
page.content: I have a brother called Thomas. My name is Louise Desborough and I am six years old. I live at Church Farm, Wenhaston and my Dad is the farmer. We grow sugar beet, barley, corn, mangles and oats. We have lots of cows that we sell for beef. My Grandad was also the farmer before my Dad. Lots of my family live in Wenhaston. I go to the primary school and I like maths, reading and English. I use the computer for all of these. The book I like best is Wind in the Willows. My favourite food is steak with chips and gravy. I also like fish, but I don't like swede or cabbage or beans, but Mum makes me eat them. We have a silver Ford car and an orange Datsun Patrol. My best friend is Carla - she is some sort of cousin.
